272
01:03:09,727 --> 01:03:12,400
Children, stop playing around!

273
01:03:12,567 --> 01:03:15,684
Who do you think
does the washing?

274
01:03:16,167 --> 01:03:19,762
Marcos! Take care of the children,
for God's sake!

275
01:03:43,127 --> 01:03:45,846
