I'll keep you in my heart.

296
01:13:53,927 --> 01:13:55,201
Goodbye.

297
01:15:01,167 --> 01:15:03,317
You forgot your jacket, Marcos.

298
01:17:05,567 --> 01:17:07,125
Take care, Marcos.

299
01:17:38,527 --> 01:17:39,562
Yes.

300
01:17:44,287 --> 01:17:46,084
